Hall,is,a,communications,platform,for,organizations,teams,and,businesses,Hall,offers,a,variety,of,communications,and,collaboration,features,such,as,group,chats,file,sharing,and,instant,messaging,on,multiple,platforms,The,Hall,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,Hall,with,other,applications,such,as,Zapier,Zendesk,Github,and,Get,Satisfaction,The,main,API,method,is,linking,Hall,to,accounts,on,these,other,applications